column2: Rabba Mere Haal Da Mehram Tu
Yeh Jo Halka Halka Saroor Hai
Aaja Neendiyan Tere Intzaar Mein-Koi Na Pooche
Besabar Besabar Hum Kyon Hain Magar
Eh Sochan Soch Ke Dil Mera
Just Another Day-Aaja Sanware Tere Naina
Mora Jiya Nahin Laage Tera Bina
Saiyyon Ni Asin Nainan De (With Commentary)
Sudh Budh Sang Le Gaya Re Jogi
Tohe Piya Milenge-Ghungat Ke Pat Khol Ni
